Bot</a><br />\n<br />\n可以去task1入面美國參議員講香港的tweets Reply講星火被凍結資產的事件<br />\n<br />\n記住twitter一定要用reply ，令外國議員見到香港最新狀況/外國媒體報導，先係衝到出國際，如果只係香港人出tweet，大家香港人不斷rt, 都剩係停留響同溫層本地圍爐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a>"},{"pid":"8b49f8686aa1bf10057a7ae3e6dde543a0baf0e1","tid":1789801,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英國先係主線呀！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【致英國及美國政府的公開信】 《中英聯合聲明》- 條約簽署之第35年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db1882e000ea2e0529c277227372d34f573196d2","tid":1789801,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},{"pid":"53de476a033c03b5698f17cec88de4a54142973f","tid":1789801,"uid":232229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8482f6df2268b67d3ae70e66cf6a4f8f8cadc3de","tid":1789801,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"5ce0d9cd610701869450c944e7d640750bca9a87","tid":1789801,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae58cd8d0637bc27459e8910b2f602e98468f2ae","tid":1789801,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:13:45.000Z","msg":"，"